 variational approaches have required strong conditions on\nthe location of the resonant point, whereas our result applies to any point in\nthe Fucik spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jul 2012 20:54:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-29"}
