\log_B n + k/B)$ I/Os.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jul 2012 13:30:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 17 Nov 2012 15:55:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-11-20"}
